#HELPS
150 sunken sanctum~
The Sunken Sanctum is an ancient ruin buried beneath a collapsed mountain.
Once a fortress of a powerful order of mages, it now crawls with the remnants
of their experiments - creatures twisted by centuries of uncontrolled magic.

Deep within the Sanctum lie hidden chambers sealed by ancient puzzles.
Those who solve them may discover paths to even more dangerous areas.

Recommended level: 150-170.
~
0 $~
#ROOMS
#9500
The Collapsed Entrance~
You stand at the edge of a massive collapse, where the mountainside has crumbled
inward to reveal a dark tunnel descending into the earth.  Broken timbers and
shattered stone litter the path leading down.  A faint cold wind rises from
below, carrying the smell of old dust and something faintly magical.
~
