E
timbers stone~
The timbers are ancient and rotted through.  Whatever held this entrance
together collapsed long ago.  Strange symbols are carved into some of the
stones -- a warning, perhaps.
~
S
#9501
The Outer Corridor~
A long corridor stretches before you, its arched ceiling blackened by old fire.
The walls are carved stone, etched with the remains of murals depicting a great
order of mages at the height of their power.  Most of the murals are defaced
or worn beyond recognition, but a few fragments remain.
~
