#9505
The Gallery of Experiments~
This side chamber is lined with glass cases, most of them shattered.  Where
the cases remain intact, you can see unsettling preserved specimens -- twisted
creatures that appear to be failed experiments.  A few Shadow Stalkers patrol
this area, drawn to the residual magical energy.
~
