#9506
The Forgotten Alcove~
A narrow side passage leads to a small alcove that has been overlooked for
centuries.  Dust lies thick on every surface, undisturbed.  Someone -- or
something -- carved a small crevice into the wall and wedged something inside
it long ago.
~
