#9507
The Crystal Laboratory~
Towering crystalline formations grow from the floor and ceiling alike, some
of them pulsing with cold inner light.  The Crystalweavers have made this
place their own, and it shows -- the air itself crackles with static, and
every surface is coated in fine crystal dust.
~
