#9508
The Eastern Corridor~
A wide passage running east to west connects the laboratory to the deeper
sanctum.  The walls here are carved with equations and arcane formulae,
inscribed by the mages who once worked here.  Some of them glow faintly,
suggesting they still hold residual power.
~
