#9510
The Riddlegolem's Secret Passage~
A narrow passage hidden behind the magical barrier leads north.  The walls
here are different -- rougher, natural stone rather than carved masonry.
It seems this passage was not part of the original construction, but was
added later -- perhaps by someone who knew the answer and wanted a private
route.
~
