#9511
The Spirit Archives~
Tall shelves of crumbling books and scrolls line every wall of this circular
chamber.  Most of the texts are too damaged to read, but a few remain intact.
Spirit Mages drift between the shelves, endlessly consulting texts that
dissolved into dust long ago.  A pale blue light fills the room from no
visible source.
~
