#9512
The Antechamber of the Vault~
A grand antechamber, its ceiling thirty feet above.  Faded tapestries hang
from iron rings, depicting the order's sigil -- a spire above a flame.
The northern wall is dominated by an enormous iron door set with rune-carved
panels.  This is the entrance to the inner vault.
~
