#9550
The Inner Vault~
The inner vault is vast and dimly lit by crystals set into the ceiling.  The
walls are lined with sealed alcoves, most of them stripped bare by whatever
disaster befell the sanctum.  In the centre of the room stands the Vaultkeeper,
and behind it, a raised dais bearing a single ornate chest -- still locked,
still waiting.
~
