chest dais~
The chest is made of some dark metal that does not tarnish.  Carved into
the lid is the order's sigil.  It is locked, and there is no keyhole -- only
a small depression the size of a fist, shaped like the outline of an idol.
~
E
alcoves walls~
Most of the alcoves are empty.  A few still hold fragments of equipment
too damaged to be useful, and one holds the desiccated remains of a mage
who apparently spent their last hours in here.
~
